### Generate JWT Token (make sure you're logged in first)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/test-jwt
Content-Type: application/json

### Verify JWT Token (replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/test-jwt
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Test with session cookie (if you have the cookie value)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/test-jwt
Cookie: better-auth.session_token=YOUR_SESSION_COOKIE_VALUE

### Example: Get orders with JWT token
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE